---
title: Creamy Dijon Chicken & Mushrooms with Thyme-Roasted Potatoes & Zucchini
description: In honor of the summer games and inspired by a gold-medal winning recipe from HF Spain, these juicy seared chicken cutlets are drizzled with a creamy, buttery mustard-herb sauce that’s infused with dried thyme and loaded with savory sautéed mushrooms, adding tangy richness to every bite. On the side are tender roasted carrots and zucchini seasoned with garlic and thyme.
